{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Server-sent events","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"documentation","title":"文件","isH3":false,"content":"<p>網頁一般來說是由客戶端向伺服器請求資料. 藉由 server-sent 事件, 伺服器在任何時候都可以向客戶端推送資料. 即將推送進來的訊息可以自客戶端上做 <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\">Events</a> + data </em>處理.</p>\n\n<table class=\"topicpage-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>\n    \n\n    <dl>\n     <dt id=\"使用\">使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events/Using_server-sent_events\">server-sent events</a></dt>\n     <dd>有關如何在伺服器端和客戶端使用 server-sent 事件的教學文章.</dd>\n     <dt id=\"參考\">參考 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource\">EventSource</a></dt>\n     <dd>關於客戶端的 EventSource API.</dd>\n    </dl>\n\n   </td>\n   <td>\n    <h2 id=\"tools\">工具</h2>\n\n    <ul>\n     <li>Remy Sharp’s <a href=\"https://github.com/remy/polyfills/blob/master/EventSource.js\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">EventSource polyfill</a></li>\n     <li>Yaffle’s <a href=\"https://github.com/Yaffle/EventSource\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">EventSource polyfill</a></li>\n     <li>Rick Waldron’s <a href=\"https://github.com/rwldrn/jquery.eventsource\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jquery plugin</a></li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2 id=\"related_topics\">相關主題</h2>\n\n    <ul>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/AJAX\">AJAX</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API\">WebSockets</a></li>\n    </ul>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/server-sent-events.html#server-sent-events","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"undefined"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>A <a href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2011/06/a-wall-powered-by-eventsource-and-server-sent-events/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Twitter like application</a> powered by server-sent events and <a href=\"https://github.com/mozilla/webowonder-demos/tree/master/demos/friends%20timeline\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">its code on Github</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://dsheiko.com/weblog/html5-and-server-sent-events\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 and Server-sent events</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://rajudasa.blogspot.in/2012/05/html5-server-sent-events-using-aspnet.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Server-sent events using Asp.Net</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"文件","id":"documentation"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"網頁一般來說是由客戶端向伺服器請求資料. 藉由 server-sent 事件, 伺服器在任何時候都可以向客戶端推送資料. 即將推送進來的訊息可以自客戶端上做 Events + data 處理.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"サーバー送信イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/server-sent_events","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/server-sent_events/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events","title":"Server-sent events"}],"pageTitle":"Server-sen